title: The National Gallery London (Orbis Art Ebook).pdf
description:
The National Gallery, London
Orbis Books | 1977 | ISBN: 0856133140 | English | 144 pages | PDF | 32 MB


London's National Gallery draws visitors from around the globe. This important new survey of the National Gallery collection includes reproductions of all the major paintings. Written by a member of the gallery staff, it provides an authoritative and up-to-date account. Recent acquisitions like Titian's Death of Actaeon and Klimt's Portrait of Hermine Gallia are included and described in detail
